{
  "info": {
    "name": "Mwork Fairness Checks (Casting Capacity + Counters + Geo)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": "Collection to verify casting capacity counters, response_count increments, and urgent geo validation. Base path is /api/v1 (see cmd/api/main.go).\n\nIMPORTANT MANUAL SETUP (if API cannot create/modify castings due to verification requirements):\n- Set collection/environment variables castingId and urgentCastingId to existing castings owned by the employer user.\n- In DB, set required_models_count=1 for castingId and ensure accepted_models_count=0 and status='active' before running acceptance checks.\n- For geo check, ensure urgentCastingId has date_from within 24h and a city different from the model profile city.\n\nRoutes used:\n- Auth: POST /auth/register, POST /auth/login\n- Profile: POST /profiles/models, POST /profiles/employers, GET /profiles/me, PUT /profiles/models/{id}\n- Casting: POST /castings (may require verified employer)\n- Responses: POST /castings/{id}/responses, PATCH /responses/{id}/status\n\nResponse bodies are wrapped in {success, data, error} (see internal/pkg/response/response.go)."
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Setup",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Model",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{modelEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{modelPassword}}\",\n  \"role\": \"model\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Register Model returns 201 or 409', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect([201, 409]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
